channel.title: Test 64-bit Windows Simba
channel.description:
I need testers with 64-bit windows to test Simba, yesterday I finally compiled a SMART plugin that I believe should work with 64-bit Simba, but now all of the sudden it seems it won't even run. If you could grab them from here:
http://www.moparisthebest.com/downloads/simba/unstable/
And find the latest one that works with 64-bit windows, so we can know which commit broke it and fix the problem.
Thanks!
